	<pre><code><span class="comment"># irrelevant facts about me</span>
<strong>personal system:</strong>  Artix Linux (OpenRC), all in
<strong>i build:</strong>          web apps, audio plugins, terminal tools
<strong>i'm into:</strong>         music production, motorsports, rhythm games
<strong>philosophy:</strong>       Keep It Simple Stupid</code></pre>

	<p>
		This site is my logbook, so it contains my notes, experiments and whatever I feel
